<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="3Sep1938"><font color="red">3 September 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  Thank you for your letter of the 1st to Mr de la Mare &hellip; I am sending the substance of your letter to the printers and hope they will now have the paging in order.  </div>
